### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Create User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alex",
  "email": "alex@example.com"
}

### Get User (replace USER_ID with actual id)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/USER_ID

### Get User Limits
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/USER_ID/limits

### Generate Lesson
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID"
}

### Generate Lesson with Topic Filter
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "topic": "Prompt Engineering"
}

### Check Answer (multiple choice)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/check-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "lessonId": "lesson_001",
  "questionId": "q1",
  "userAnswer": 1
}

### Check Answer (true/false)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/check-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "lessonId": "lesson_001",
  "questionId": "q2",
  "userAnswer": true
}

### Check Answer (fill_blank)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/lessons/check-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "lessonId": "lesson_001",
  "questionId": "q4",
  "userAnswer": "role"
}

### Save Progress
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "lessonId": "lesson_001",
  "correctCount": 4,
  "totalCount": 5
}

### Save Perfect Progress
POST http://localhost:3000/api/progress/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID",
  "lessonId": "lesson_002",
  "correctCount": 5,
  "totalCount": 5
}

### Get Progress
GET http://localhost:3000/api/progress/USER_ID
